Write code which uses if then else statement to check if  a given balance is greater or lesser than the minimum
balance . Write a class BankCheck with public method checkBalance that takes one parameter balance of type double.Use if then else statement and
print Balance is low if balance is less than 1000 otherwise  print sufficient balance.
import java.util.*;
class Array{
    public static void main(String args[]){
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        System.out.println("Salary is : ");
        int salary = sc.nextInt();
        if(salary<1000){
            System.out.println("Less than minimum salary:");
        }
        else if(salary==1000){
            System.out.println("Salary is minimum :");
        }
        else{
          System.out.println("Salary is sufficient :");   
        }
    }
}
